Diary kept while on survey for railroad route from the Mississippi River to the Pacific Ocean in 1853-1854; 
      	covers period from Jan. 3-Feb. 20, 1854. Accompanied by a typescript and photocopy of the diary and Tidball's 
      	personal copy, presented by Whipple, of Vol. 3 of the published Report, annotated by Tidball.
